        Parameters:

        excludeCancelled - If true, cancelled jobs will not be returned. A job may be in cancelled state if a cancel request has arrived but it has not been removed from queue yet (e.g. still running).
        exclude - Ids of jobs to ignore in the result
        tags - The list of tags
